INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(2948,'fortunes',127,'Every nonzero finite dimensional inner product space has an orthonormal basis.

It makes sense, when you don''t think about it.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(2949,'fortunes',312,'Every now and then when your life gets complicated and the weasels
start closing in, the only cure is to load up on heinous chemicals and
then drive like a bastard from Hollywood to Las Vegas ... with the
music at top volume and at least a pint of ether.
		-- Hunter S. Thompson, "Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(2950,'fortunes',394,'Every one says that politicians lie all the time, and that just isn''t so!
But you do have to understand body language to know when they''re lying and
when they aren''t.

	When a politician rubs his nose, he isn''t lying.
	When a politician tugs on his ear, he isn''t lying.
	When a politician scratches his collar bone, he isn''t lying.
	When his mouth starts moving, that''s when he''s lying!');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(2951,'fortunes',229,'Every paper published in a respectable journal should have a preface by
