INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11520,'fortunes',706,'When my freshman roommate at Cornell found out I was Jewish, she was,
at her request, moved to a different room.  She told me she didn''t
think she had ever seen a Jew before.  My only response was to begin
wearing a small Star of David on a chain around my neck.  I had not
become a more observing Jew; rather, discovering that the label of
Jew was offensive to others made me want to let people know who I
was and what I believed in.  Similarly, after talking to these young
women -- one of whom told me that she didn''t think she had ever met
a feminist -- I''ve taken to identifying myself as a feminist in the
most unlikely of situations.
		-- Susan Bolotin, "Voices From the Post-Feminist Generation"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11521,'fortunes',113,'When neither their poverty nor their honor is
touched, the majority of men live content.
		-- Niccolo Machiavelli');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11522,'fortunes',44,'When nothing can possibly go wrong, it will.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11523,'fortunes',80,'When one burns one''s bridges, what a very nice fire it makes.
		-- Dylan Thomas');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11524,'fortunes',98,'When one knows women one pities men,
but when one studies men, one excuses women.
		-- Horne Tooke');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11525,'fortunes',99,'When one wants to get rid of an unsupportable pressure, one needs hashish.
		-- Friedrich Nietzsche');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11526,'fortunes',195,'When one woman was asked how long she had been going to symphony concerts,
she paused to calculate and replied, "Forty-seven years -- and I find I mind
it less and less."
		-- Louise Andrews Kent');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11527,'fortunes',241,'When operating the diopter adjustment knob with your eye to the view-
finder, be careful not to put your fingers or fingernails in your eye.
		-- found in the users manual of the Nikon D2x camera,
		   a camera for professional photographers');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11528,'fortunes',231,'When Oxygen Tech played Hydrogen U.
The Game had just begun, when Hydrogen scored two fast points
And Oxygen still had none
Then Oxygen scored a single goal
And thus it did remain, At Hydrogen 2 and Oxygen 1
Called because of rain.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11529,'fortunes',92,'When people have trouble communicating,
the least they can do is to shut up.
		-- Tom Lehrer');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11530,'fortunes',62,'When people say nothing, they don''t necessarily mean nothing.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11531,'fortunes',49,'When pleasure remains, does it remain a pleasure?');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11532,'fortunes',735,'When President Paul Doumer of France was assassinated in Paris in 1932,
newspapers differed in their versions of the event.  This is from "Paris
was Yesterday: 1925-1939" by Janet Flanner, edited by Irving Drutman.

	Taste varied as to his cry when he was shot down, the more popular
	papers preferring his despairing "Oh, la la!," the graver dailies
	favoring "Is it possible?"  What few reported were his dying words:
	"But what kind of chauffeur was it?"  Having been told by his aides
	not that he had been shot but that he had been struck by a taxi, the
	President spent the last conscious moments of his life wondering how
	an automobile got into the charity book sale at the Maison
	Rothschild, where his assassination occurred.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11533,'fortunes',210,'When properly administered, vacations do not diminish productivity: for
every week you''re away and get nothing done, there''s another when your boss
is away and you get twice as much done.
		-- Daniel B. Luten');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11534,'fortunes',115,'When smashing monuments, save the pedestals -- they always come in handy.
		-- Stanislaw J. Lec, "Unkempt Thoughts"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11535,'fortunes',113,'When some people decide it''s time for everyone to make
big changes, it means that they want you to change first.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11536,'fortunes',103,'When some people discover the truth, they just
can''t understand why everybody isn''t eager to hear it.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11537,'fortunes',867,'When someone makes a move		We''ll send them all we''ve got,
Of which we don''t approve,		John Wayne and Randolph Scott,
Who is it that always intervenes?	Remember those exciting fighting scenes?
U.N. and O.A.S.,			To the shores of Tripoli,
They have their place, I guess,		But not to Mississippoli,
But first, send the Marines!		What do we do?  We send the Marines!

For might makes right,			Members of the corps
And till they''ve seen the light,	All hate the thought of war:
They''ve got to be protected,		They''d rather kill them off by
						peaceful means.
All their rights respected,		Stop calling it aggression--
Till somebody we like can be elected.	We hate that expression!
					We only want the world to know
					That we support the status quo;
					They love us everywhere we go,
					So when in doubt, send the Marines!
		-- Tom Lehrer, "Send The Marines"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11538,'fortunes',113,'When someone says "I want a programming language in
which I need only say what I wish done," give him a lollipop.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11539,'fortunes',84,'When speculation has done its worst, two plus two still equals four.
		-- S. Johnson');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11540,'fortunes',69,'When taxes are due, Americans tend to feel quite bled-white and blue.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11541,'fortunes',649,'When the Apple IIc was introduced, the informative copy led off with a couple
of asterisked sentences:

	It weighs less than 8 pounds.*
	And costs less than $1,300.**

In tiny type were these "fuller explanations":

      * Don''t asterisks make you suspicious as all get out?  Well, all
	this means is that the IIc alone weights 7.5 pounds. The power
	pack, monitor, an extra disk drive, a printer and several bricks
	will make the IIc weigh more. Our lawyers were concerned that you
	might not be able to figure this out for yourself.

     ** The FTC is concerned about price fixing. You can pay more if
	you really want to.  Or less.
		-- Forbes');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11542,'fortunes',95,'When the ax entered the forest, the trees said, "The handle is one of us!"
		-- Turkish proverb');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11543,'fortunes',86,'When the blind lead the blind they will both fall over the cliff.
		-- Chinese proverb');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11544,'fortunes',91,'When the bosses talk about improving productivity, they are never talking
about themselves.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11545,'fortunes',58,'When the candles are out all women are fair.
		-- Plutarch');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11546,'fortunes',37,'When the cup is full, carry it level.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11547,'fortunes',105,'When the doubt vanishes and the issue becomes evident, stupidity reigns.
		-- Poul Henningsen (1894-1967)');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11548,'fortunes',75,'When the English language gets in my way, I walk over it.
		-- Billy Sunday');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11549,'fortunes',112,'When the fog came in on little cat feet last night, it left these little
muddy paw prints on the hood of my car.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11550,'fortunes',54,'When the going gets tough, everyone leaves.
		-- Lynch');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11551,'fortunes',68,'When the going gets tough, the tough get empirical.
		-- Jon Carroll');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11552,'fortunes',52,'When the going gets tough, the tough go grab a beer.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11553,'fortunes',49,'When the going gets tough, the tough go shopping.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11554,'fortunes',70,'When the going gets weird, the weird turn pro.
		-- Hunter S. Thompson');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11555,'fortunes',105,'When the government bureau''s remedies do not match
your problem, you modify the problem, not the remedy.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11556,'fortunes',343,'When the Guru administers, the users
are hardly aware that he exists.
Next best is a sysop who is loved.
Next, one who is feared.
And worst, one who is despised.

If you don''t trust the users,
you make them untrustworthy.

The Guru doesn''t talk, he hacks.
When his work is done,
the users say, "Amazing:
we implemented it, all by ourselves!"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11557,'fortunes',299,'When the leaders speak of peace
The common folk know
That war is coming
When the leaders curse war
The mobilization order is already written out.

Every day, to earn my daily bread
I go to the market where lies are bought
Hopefully
I take my place among the sellers.
		-- Bertolt Brecht, "Hollywood"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11558,'fortunes',250,'When the Ngdanga tribe of West Africa hold their moon love ceremonies,
the men of the tribe bang their heads on sacred trees until they get a
nose bleed, which usually cures them of _t_h_a_t.
		-- Mike Harding, "The Armchair Anarchist''s Almanac"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11559,'fortunes',82,'When the only tool you have is a hammer, every problem starts to look
like a nail.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11560,'fortunes',79,'When the President does it, that means it is not illegal.
		-- Richard M. Nixon');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11561,'fortunes',45,'When the revolution comes, count your change.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11562,'fortunes',323,'When the salesman''s car broke down, he walked to the nearest farmhouse to ask
if he could stay the night.  The farmer agreed to put him up.  "I live alone,"
he continued, "you can have the bedroom at the top of the stairs, to the
right."
	"Oh, never mind," the disappointed salesman said. "I think I''m in
the wrong joke."');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11563,'fortunes',100,'When the speaker and he to whom he is speaking do not understand, that is
metaphysics.
		-- Voltaire');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11564,'fortunes',49,'When the sun shineth, make hay.
		-- John Heywood');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11565,'fortunes',345,'When the Universe was not so out of whack as it is today, and all the
stars were lined up in their proper places, you could easily count them
from left to right, or top to bottom, and the larger and bluer ones
were set apart, and the smaller yellowing types pushed off to the
corners as bodies of a lower grade ...
		-- Stanislaw Lem, "Cyberiad"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11566,'fortunes',621,'When the usher noticed a man stretched across three seats in a movie theatre,
he walked over and whispered, "I''m sorry, sir, but you''re allowed only a single
seat." The man moaned, but did not budge.  "Sir," the user said more loudly,
"if you don''t move, I''ll have to call a manager."  The man moaned again but
stayed where he was. The usher left, and returned with the manager, who, after
several more attempts at dislodging the fellow, called the police.
	The cop took a look at the reclining man and said, "All right, boyo,
what''s your name?"
	"Samuel," he mumbled.
	"And where''re you from, Sam?"
	"The balcony."');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11567,'fortunes',104,'When the weight of the paperwork equals the weight of the plane, the
plane will fly.
		-- Donald Douglas');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11568,'fortunes',75,'When the wind is great, bow before it;
when the wind is heavy, yield to it.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11569,'fortunes',176,'When there are two conflicting versions of the story, the wise course
is to believe the one in which people appear at their worst.
		-- H. Allen Smith, "Let the Crabgrass Grow"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11570,'fortunes',89,'When there is an old maid in the house, a watch dog is unnecessary.
		-- Honore de Balzac');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11571,'fortunes',84,'When things go well, expect something to
explode, erode, collapse or just disappear.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11572,'fortunes',285,'When two people are under the influence of the most violent, most
insane, most delusive, and most transient of passions, they are
required to swear that they will remain in that excited, abnormal, and
exhausting condition continuously until death do them part.
		-- George Bernard Shaw');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11573,'fortunes',643,'When users see one GUI as beautiful,
other user interfaces become ugly.
When users see some programs as winners,
other programs become lossage.

Pointers and NULLs reference each other.
High level and assembler depend on each other.
Double and float cast to each other.
High-endian and low-endian define each other.
While and until follow each other.

Therefore the Guru
programs without doing anything
and teaches without saying anything.
Warnings arise and he lets them come;
processes are swapped and he lets them go.
He has but doesn''t possess,
acts but doesn''t expect.
When his work is done, he deletes it.
That is why it lasts forever.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11574,'fortunes',105,'When we are planning for posterity,
we ought to remember that virtue is not hereditary.
		-- Thomas Paine');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11575,'fortunes',302,'When we jumped into Sicily, the units became separated, and I couldn''t find
anyone.  Eventually I stumbled across two colonels, a major, three captains,
two lieutenants, and one rifleman, and we secured the bridge.  Never in the
history of war have so few been led by so many.
		-- General James Gavin');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11576,'fortunes',41,'When we talk of tomorrow, the gods laugh.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11577,'fortunes',165,'When we understand knowledge-based systems, it will be as before --
except our fingertips will have been singed.
		-- Epigrams in Programming, ACM SIGPLAN Sept. 1982');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11578,'fortunes',72,'When we write programs that "learn",
it turns out we do and they don''t.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11579,'fortunes',103,'When women kiss it always reminds one of prize fighters shaking hands.
		-- H. L. Mencken, "Sententiae"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11580,'fortunes',167,'When women love us, they forgive us everything, even our crimes;
when they do not love us, they give us credit for nothing, not
even our virtues.
		-- Honore de Balzac');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11581,'fortunes',112,'When you are about to die, a wombat is better than no company at all.
		-- Roger Zelazny, "Doorways in the Sand"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11582,'fortunes',244,'When you are about to do an objective and scientific piece of investigation
of a topic, it is well to have the answer firmly in hand, so that you can
proceed forthrightly, without being deflected or swayed, directly to the
goal.
		-- Amrom Katz');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11583,'fortunes',114,'When you are at Rome live in the Roman style;
when you are elsewhere live as they live elsewhere.
		-- St. Ambrose');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11584,'fortunes',57,'When you are in it up to your ears, keep your mouth shut.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11585,'fortunes',59,'When you are working hard, get up and retch every so often.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11586,'fortunes',718,'When you are young, you enjoy a sustained illusion that sooner or later
something marvelous is going to happen, that you are going to transcend
your parents'' limitations...  At the same time, you feel sure that in all
the wilderness of possibility; in all the forests of opinion, there is a
vital something that can be known -- known and grasped.  That we will
eventually know it, and convert the whole mystery into a coherent
narrative.  So that then one''s true life -- the point of everything --
will emerge from the mist into a pure light, into total comprehension.
But it isn''t like that at all.  But if it isn''t, where did the idea come
from, to torture and unsettle us?
		-- Brian Aldiss, "Helliconia Summer"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11587,'fortunes',82,'When you become used to never being alone,
you may consider yourself Americanized.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11588,'fortunes',57,'When you dial a wrong number you never get a busy signal.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11589,'fortunes',78,'When you die, you lose a very important part of your life.
		-- Brooke Shields');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11590,'fortunes',74,'When you dig another out of trouble,
you''ve got a place to bury your own.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11591,'fortunes',60,'When you don''t know what to do, walk fast and look worried.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11592,'fortunes',54,'When you don''t know what you are doing, do it neatly.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11593,'fortunes',284,'When you find yourself in danger,
When you''re threatened by a stranger,
When it looks like you will take a lickin''...

There is one thing you should learn,
When there is no one else to turn to,
	Caaaall for Super Chicken!!  (**bwuck-bwuck-bwuck-bwuck**)
	Caaaall for Super Chicken!!');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11594,'fortunes',1082,'When you get what you want in your struggle for pelf,
And the world makes you King for a day,
Then go to the mirror and look at yourself,
And see what that guy has to say.
	For it isn''t your Father, or Mother, or Wife,
	Who judgement upon you must pass.
	The feller whose verdict counts most in your life
	Is the guy staring back from the glass.
He''s the feller to please, never mind all the rest,
For he''s with you clear up to the end,
And you''ve passed your most dangerous, difficult test
If the guy in the glass is your friend.
	You may be like Jack Horner and "chisel" a plum,
	And think you''re a wonderful guy,
	But the man in the glass says you''re only a bum
	If you can''t look him straight in the eye.
You can fool the whole world down the pathway of years,
And get pats on the back as you pass,
But your final reward will be heartaches and tears
If you''ve cheated the guy in the glass.
		-- "The Guy in the Glass"
		   Copyright 1934, Dale Wimbrow (1895-1954)
		   [Pelf is a Middle English word for wealth or riches,
		    especially when acquired dishonestly. Ed.]');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11595,'fortunes',148,'When you go into court you are putting your fate into the hands of twelve
people who weren''t smart enough to get out of jury duty.
		-- Norm Crosby');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11596,'fortunes',48,'When you go out to buy, don''t show your silver.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11597,'fortunes',84,'When you have an efficient government, you have a dictatorship.
		-- Harry S. Truman');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11598,'fortunes',138,'When you have eliminated the impossible, whatever
remains, however improbable, must be the truth.
		-- Sherlock Holmes, "The Sign of Four"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11599,'fortunes',260,'When you have shot and killed a man you have in some measure
clarified your attitude toward him.  You have given a definite
answer to a definite problem.  For better or worse you have
acted decisively.  In a way, the next move is up to him.
		-- R. A. Lafferty');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11600,'fortunes',112,'When you have to kill a man it costs nothing to be polite.
		-- Winston Churchill, on formal declarations of war');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11601,'fortunes',124,'When you jump for joy, beware that no-one
moves the ground from beneath your feet.
		-- Stanislaw J. Lec, "Unkempt Thoughts"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11602,'fortunes',189,'When you know absolutely nothing about the topic, make your forecast by
asking a carefully selected probability sample of 300 others who don''t
know the answer either.
		-- Edgar R. Fiedler');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11603,'fortunes',71,'When you live in a sick society,
just about everything you do is wrong.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11604,'fortunes',99,'When you make your mark in the world,
watch out for guys with erasers.
		-- The Wall Street Journal');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11605,'fortunes',158,'When you meet a master swordsman,
show him your sword.
When you meet a man who is not a poet,
do not show him your poem.
		-- Rinzai, ninth century Zen master');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11606,'fortunes',383,'When you overesteem great hackers,
more users become cretins.
When you develop encryption,
more users become crackers.

The Guru leads
by emptying user''s minds
and increasing their quotas,
by weakening their ambition
and toughening their resolve.
When users lack knowledge and desire,
management will not try to interfere.

Practice not-looping,
and everything will fall into place.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11607,'fortunes',158,'When you say that you agree to a thing in principle, you mean that
you have not the slightest intention of carrying it out in practice.
		-- Otto von Bismarck');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11608,'fortunes',118,'When you speak to others for their own good it''s advice;
when they speak to you for your own good it''s interference.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11609,'fortunes',89,'When you try to make an impression, the
chances are that is the impression you will make.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11610,'fortunes',51,'When you were born, a big chance was taken for you.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11611,'fortunes',112,'When your conscious becomes unconscious, you are drunk.
When your unconscious becomes conscious, you are stoned.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11612,'fortunes',168,'When your life is a leaf that the seasons tear off and condemn
They will bind you with love that is graceful and green as a stem.
		-- Leonard Cohen, "Sisters of Mercy"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11613,'fortunes',33,'When your memory goes, forget it!');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11614,'fortunes',72,'When your work speaks for itself, don''t interrupt.
		-- Henry J. Kaiser');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11615,'fortunes',199,'When you''re a Yup
You''re a Yup all the way
From your first slice of Brie
To your last Cabernet.

When you''re a Yup
You''re not just a dreamer
You''re making things happen
You''re driving a Beamer.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11616,'fortunes',207,'When you''re away, I''m restless, lonely
Wretched, bored, dejected, only
Here''s the rub, my darling dear,
I feel the same when you are near.
		-- Samuel Hoffenstein, "Poems in Praise of Practically Nothing"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11617,'fortunes',95,'When you''re bored with yourself, marry, and be bored with someone else.
		-- David Pryce-Jones');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11618,'fortunes',83,'When you''re dining out and you suspect
something''s wrong, you''re probably right.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11619,'fortunes',77,'When you''re down and out, lift up your
voice and shout, "I''M DOWN AND OUT"!');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11620,'fortunes',53,'When you''re in command, command.
		-- Admiral Nimitz');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11621,'fortunes',228,'When you''re married to someone, they take you for granted ... when
you''re living with someone it''s fantastic ... they''re so frightened
of losing you they''ve got to keep you satisfied all the time.
		-- Nell Dunn, "Poor Cow"');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11622,'fortunes',67,'When you''re not looking at it, this fortune is written in FORTRAN.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11623,'fortunes',69,'When you''re ready to give up the struggle, who can you surrender to?');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11624,'fortunes',174,'WHEN YOU''RE RIDING IN A TIME MACHINE way far into the future, don''t stick
your elbow out the window or it''ll turn into a fossil.
		-- Jack Handey, "The New Mexican" (1988)');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11625,'fortunes',222,'WHENEVER ANYBODY SAYS he''s struggling to become a human being I have to
laugh because the apes beat him to it by about a million years.  Struggle
to become a parrot or something.
		-- Jack Handey, "The New Mexican" (1988)');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11626,'fortunes',86,'Whenever anyone says, "theoretically," they really mean "not really".
		-- Dave Parnas');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11627,'fortunes',113,'Whenever I date a guy, I think, is this the man I want my children
to spend their weekends with?
		-- Rita Rudner');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11628,'fortunes',67,'Whenever I feel like exercise, I lie down until the feeling passes.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11629,'fortunes',123,'Whenever I hear anyone arguing for slavery, I feel
a strong impulse to see it tried on him personally.
		-- Abraham Lincoln');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11630,'fortunes',207,'Whenever I see an old lady slip and fall on a wet sidewalk, my first instinct
is to laugh.  But then I think, what if I was an ant, and she fell on me.
Then it wouldn''t seem quite so funny.
		-- Jack Handey');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11631,'fortunes',77,'Whenever people agree with me I always feel I must be wrong.
		-- Oscar Wilde');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(11632,'fortunes',713,'Whenever Richard Cory went downtown,
	We people on the pavement looked at him:
He was a gentleman from sole to crown,
	Clean-favored, and imperially slim.
And he was always quietly arrayed,
	And he was always human when he talked;
But still he fluttered pulses when he said,
	"Good morning," and he glittered when he walked.
And he was rich -- yes, richer than a king --
	And admirably schooled in every grace:
In fine, we thought that he was everything
	To make us wish that we were in his place.
So on we worked, and waited for the light,
	And went without the meat, and cursed the bread;
And Richard Cory, one calm summer night,
	Went home and put a bullet through his head.
		-- E. A. Robinson, "Richard Cory"');
