		   [No, it wasn''t John F. Kennedy.  Ed.]');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(12249,'fortunes',343,'You see, wire telegraph is a kind of a very, very long cat.  You pull
his tail in New York and his head is meowing in Los Angeles.  Do you
understand this?  And radio operates exactly the same way:  you send
signals here, they receive them there.  The only difference is that
there is no cat.
		-- Albert Einstein, when asked to describe radio');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(12250,'fortunes',72,'You seek to shield those you love
