something.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(14090,'murphy',220,'When traveling overseas, the exchange rate improves
markedly the day after one has purchased foreign
currency.

Upon returning home, the exchange rate drops again as
soon as one has converted all unused foreign currency.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(14091,'murphy',97,'When we try to pick out anything by itself we find
it hitched to everything else in the universe.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(14092,'murphy',134,'When working toward the solution of a problem,
it always helps if you know the answer.
