the uninformed.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(14111,'murphy',168,'You are always complimented on the item which took the
least effort to prepare.

Example:
	If you make "duck a l''orange" you will be
	complimented on the baked potato.');
INSERT INTO "fortune_fortune" VALUES(14112,'murphy',65,'You are not drunk if you can lay on the floor without
